name: Blueberry Afgoo
description: Blueberry Afgoo is an Indica-dominant hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Blueberry and Afgoo. Bred by Fitchburg, Blueberry Afgoo is 12% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for beginner cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Blueberry Afgoo effects make them feel tingly, sleepy, and happy. Medical marijuana patients often choose Blueberry Afgoo when dealing with symptoms associated with pain, inflammation, and insomnia. The dominant terpene of this cannabis strain is caryophyllene. Blueberry Afgoo features a berry aroma and flavor profile of blueberry, and chemicals.
